BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260514T060600
DTEND:20260514T074800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.416ft at 06:06\n-2.946ft at 07:48\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Another nice shot of SSW Southern Hemi rolls in\, along with some shorter-
 period WNW swell. That's good for widespread waist to shoulder high+ waves
 \, while focal points are hitting a foot overhead. Favorable early morning
  tide push. \n\nLight S winds due much of the morning\, turn to light+/per
 iodically more SW onshores for the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
